## 6. Alerts / Notifications
- PSI > 0.2 → notify Model Owner
- Disparate Impact < 0.8 → pause deployment, initiate mitigation
- Latency > SLA → escalate to Ops

## 7. Observations / Notes
- Observed seasonal spike in data → retraining scheduled
- Monitoring frequency: Daily (metrics), Weekly (fairness), Monthly 
